room_title: Escape room "Omega Hour" by Twisted Limits Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_description: A mysterious invitation has compelled you to attend an upscale New Year's Eve party high in the city's skyline. An unidentified eccentric billionaire has quite the enticing offer for you and your friends. After an evening of lavish indulgence, you are summoned to the residence's dining quarters. As the clock nears 11:00 pm, a toast is proposed signaling your host's true intentions: The Omega Hour.
